            "body": "Oh. You are referring to the `flaskr` application.  This one intentionally allows embedding HTML.  It's operating in a trusted environment.  It uses the `|safe` filter to explicitly disable the default escaping.  Just don't use that if you don't want HTML embedded.\n"
